A player has a predefined list of tracks
It can be started
It can skip forward and backward between tracks
It can be stopped to return it to the start
It cannot rewind before the start
By default it will stop after the final track
If loop is set then the first track will play after the final track


Extra:
Each track can have a duration
It can have a randomise setting where the next track to play is random
It can have jukebox functionality where you can select a track